{"tid":1819032,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"各位香港人 大家休息左咁耐 係咪應該諗下前路","createTime":"2020-01-10T12:05:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-10T12:12:08.000Z","uid":89353,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"e6265e21d2b7e36f8d741020b2cae2c982fe6c62","tid":1819032,"uid":89353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T12:05:21.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">大家都休息左咁耐啦<br />\n好多人係poly之後只係參與過1.1<br />\n到咗今日第一覺唔覺得我哋已經開始過返正常嘅生活<br />\n係我哋會做出文宣色黃店<br />\n但係同樣地<strong>吃喝玩樂</strong>嘅人多咗<br />\n<br />\n大家仲記唔記得六月<br />\n果種氣憤嗰種絕望<br />\n大家會一齊團結出去<br />\n大家會目標一致<br />\n<br />\n但係到咗今日大家好似變返雨傘革命最後果斷階段咁<br />\n開始變咗嘉年華<br />\n講好咗我哋唔會重複犯同樣嘅錯？<br />\n講好咗今次要光復香港？<br />\n<br />\n六月我哋啲勇武一直等緊啲和理非升級<br />\n會不停升級口號<br />\n不停升級行動<br />\n但係到咗今日<br />\n升級武器嘅係警方<br />\n俾人拉嘅係勇武<br />\n甚至連公務員教職員都開始受到清算<br />\n五大訴求我地做左幾多<br />\n光復左香港未<br />\n講好咗嘅時代革命呢<br />\n我哋又話報仇嘅<br />\n<br />\n依家做左啲咩<br />\n和理非就割勇武<br />\n個個就玩分化<br />\n我哋依家輸緊呀知唔知呀<br />\n仲休息？<br />\n和理非升級未呀？</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">希望大家仲記得初衷記得自己講過嘅記得承諾過嘅</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港 時代革命<br />\n沒有暴動 只有暴政<br />\n不自由 毋寧死<br />\n寧為玉碎 不為瓦全<br />\n香港人 報仇<br />\n不割蓆 不篤灰 不分化</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n希望勇武們仲等到光復香港既日子<br />\n希望和理非係燒到自己之前識得升級啦"},{"pid":"eb468a6df4b231ef9facca3bc54bed58a0ca9d24","tid":1819032,"uid":135277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T12:06:18.000Z","msg":"大家俾d意見睇下點做"},{"pid":"3a5bc60d7f7799c80ce547b7b2c6a5b8dbddd371","tid":1819032,"uid":213952,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T12:07:20.000Z","msg":"你做左咩咁把炮"},{"pid":"77c2e47523fd80e15ac0b32bc3f396a2bac2fd17","tid":1819032,"uid":89353,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T12:08:46.000Z","msg":"延伸閱讀：香港人雨革嘅反思<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ZubvzTs9uJ4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FZubvzTs9uJ4&d=rH9paZ2ORyePGAAUSKfbjQ%2BnBs0jvEEXkL0KxwFTSeM%3D&h=c0fb8cc7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ZubvzTs9uJ4</a>"},{"pid":"aef262c74315c78672f360cd7508c12e0c692d94","tid":1819032,"uid":345458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T12:09:54.000Z","msg":"麻煩大家幫手推下呢個post <br />\n等更多對於工運未好了解嘅手足睇到！<br />\n<br />\n「警世」請重視工運戰線！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1818981\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1818981</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"3d2bcc3dce3c80115d504e3a11d4a7efd41de0e2","tid":1819032,"uid":89353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3a5bc60d7f7799c80ce547b7b2c6a5b8dbddd371","tid":1819032,"uid":213952,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T12:07:20.000Z","msg":"你做左咩咁把炮"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T12:10:21.000Z","msg":"起一起你就知咩料啦 五毛 <br />\n唔好諗住Chok我啦on9"},{"pid":"957c6da58118440b05e5d57172279dc1f74c2b34","tid":1819032,"uid":112748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T12:10:39.000Z","msg":"苦行抗爭一早就過時，適時放鬆係可以的，同埋有日程表，自已選擇參與否"},{"pid":"cae4009e02066ab8f330c1f98887c6ac5293ce93","tid":1819032,"uid":343361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T12:11:23.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">消烕曱狗甴<br />\n清除藍屍<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"f945fe6487455c70e5175e430af155ef030261fa","tid":1819032,"uid":112748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3d2bcc3dce3c80115d504e3a11d4a7efd41de0e2","tid":1819032,"uid":89353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3a5bc60d7f7799c80ce547b7b2c6a5b8dbddd371","tid":1819032,"uid":213952,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T12:07:20.000Z","msg":"你做左咩咁把炮"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T12:10:21.000Z","msg":"起一起你就知咩料啦 五毛 <br />\n唔好諗住Chok我啦on9"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T12:11:25.000Z","msg":"我早就